  string
  line 1
  line `THE AADHAAR (TARGETED DELIVERY OF FINANCIAL AND OTHER SUBSIDIES,`
  line `BENEFITS AND SERVICES) ACT, 2016`
  line ______
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line __________
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `E NROLMENT`
  line `3. Aadhaar number.`
  line `3A. Aadhaar number of children.`
  line `4. Properties of Aadhaar number.`
  line `5. Special measures for issuance of Aadhaar number to certain category of persons.`
  line `6. Update of certain information.`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `A UTHENTICATION`
  line `7. Proof of Aadhaar number necessary for receipt of certain subsidies, benefits and services, etc.`
  line `8. Authentication of Aadhaar number.`
  line `8A. Offline verification of Aadhaar number.`
  line `9. Aadhaar number not evidence of citizenship or domicile, etc.`
  line `10. Central Identities Data Repository.`
  line `CHAPTER IV`
  line `U NIQUE I DENTIFICATION A UTHORITYOF I ND I A`
  line `11. Establishment of Authority.`
  line `12. Composition of Authority.`
  line `13. Qualifications for appointment of Chairperson and Members of Authority.`
  line `14. Term of office and other conditions of service of Chairperson and Members.`
  line `15. Removal of Chairperson and Members.`
  line `16. Restrictions on Chairperson or Members on employment after cessation of office.`
  line `17. Functions of Chairperson.`
