  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_23_footnotes
  sourcePage 23
obj_root_law_sections_23_content:
  string
  line 23
  line `( b ) the salary and allowances payable to, and other terms and conditions of serv ice of, the`
  line `Chairperson and the allowances or remuneration payable to Members of the Authority under`
  line `sub - section ( 4 ) of section 14;`
  line `( c ) the other powers and functions of the Chairperson of the Authority under section 17;`
  line `( d) the other powers and functions of the Authority under clause ( t ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of`
  line `section 23;`
  line `( e ) the form of annual statement of accounts to be prepared by Authority under sub - section ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 26;`
  line `( f ) the form and the manner in which and the time within which returns and statements and`
  line `particulars are to be furnished under sub - section ( 1 ) of section 27;`
  line `( g ) the form and the manner and the time at which the Authority shall furnish annual report under`
  line `sub - section ( 2 ) of section 27;`
  line `1 [( ga ) the qualification and experience of, and the manner of appointment of, the Adjudicating`
  line `Officer under sub - section (1) of section 33B;`
  line `( gb ) the fo rm, manner, and fee for an appeal to be filed under sub - section ( 2 ) of se ction 33C;]`
  line `( h ) any other matter which is required to be, or may be, prescribed, or in respect of which`
  line `provision is to b e or may be made by rules.`
  line `54. Power of Authority to make regulations. — ( 1 ) The Authority may, by notification, make`
  line `regulations consistent with this Act and the rules made thereunder, for carrying out the provisions of this`
  line Act.
  line `( 2 ) In particular, and without prejudice to the generality of the foregoing power, such regulations may`
  line `provide for all or any of the following matters, na mely: —`
  line `2 [( a ) the entities or group of entities in the Aadhaar ecosystem under clause ( aa ), the biometric`
  line `information under clause ( g ) and the demographic information under clause ( k ), the process of`
  line `collecting demographic information and biometric informat ion from the individuals by enrolling`
  line `agencies under clause ( m ), and the modes of offline verification of Aadhaar number holder under`
  line `clause ( pa ) of section 2;]`
  line `( b ) the manner of verifying the demographic information and biometric information for issue of`
  line `Aadhaar number under sub - section ( 3 ) of section 3;`
  line `3 [( ba ) the manner of generating an alternative virtual identity under sub - section ( 4 ) of section 3;`
  line `( bb ) the manner in which cancellation of an Aadhaar number may be carried out under sub - section`
  line `( 2 ) of section 3A;]`
  line `( c ) the conditions for accepting an Aadhaar number as proof of identity of the Aadhaar number`
  line `holder under sub - section ( 3 ) of section 4;`
  line `3 [( ca ) standards of privacy and security to be complied with by the requesting entities under`
  line `sub - section ( 4 ) of section 4;`
  line `( cb ) the classification of requesting entities under sub - section ( 5 ) of section 4;]`
  line `( d ) the other categories of individuals under section 5 for whom the Authority shall take special`
  line `measures for allotment of Aadhaar number;`
  line `( e ) the manner of updating biometric information and demographic information under section 6;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 14 of 2019, s. 23 (w.e.f. 25 - 7 - 2019).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 24, ibid., for clause ( a ) (w.e.f. 25 - 7 - 2019).`
  line `3. Ins. by s. 24, ibid, (w.e.f. 25 - 7 - 2019).`
obj_root_law_sections_23_footnotes:
