  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_24_footnotes
  sourcePage 24
obj_root_law_sections_24_content:
  string
  line 24
  line `( f ) the procedure for authentication of the Aadhaar number under section 8;`
  line `1 [( fa ) the alternate and viable means of identification of individual under the proviso to clause ( b )`
  line `of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 8;`
  line `( fb ) the manner of obtaining consent under clause ( a ) of sub - section ( 2 ), the manner of providing`
  line `information to the individual undergoing offline verification under sub - section (3), and the obliga tions`
  line `of offline verification - seeking entities under clause ( c ) of sub - section ( 4 ) of section 8A;]`
  line `( g ) the other functions to be performed by the Central Identities Data Repository under section 10;`
  line `( h ) the time and places of meetings of the Authority and the procedure for transaction of business`
  line `to be followed by it, including the quorum, under sub - section ( 1 ) of section 19;`
  line `( i ) the salary and allowances payable to, and other terms and conditions of service of, the chief`
  line `executive officer, officers and other employees of the Authority under sub - section ( 2 ) of section 21;`
  line `( j ) the demographic information and biometric information under clause ( a ) and the manner of`
  line `their collection under clause ( b ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( k ) the manner of maintai ning and updating the information of individuals in the Central Identities`
  line `Data Repository under clause ( f ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( l ) the manner of omitting and deactivating an Aadhaar number and information relating thereto`
  line `under clause ( g ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( m ) the manner of use of Aadhaar numbers for the purposes of providing or availing of various`
  line `subsidies, benefits, services and other purposes for which Aadhaar numbers may be used under clause`
  line `( h ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of sect ion 23;`
  line `( n ) the terms and conditions for appointment of Registrars, enrolling agencies and other service`
  line `providers and the revocation of appointments thereof under clause ( i ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( o ) the manner of sharing information of Aadhaa r number holder under clause ( k ) of sub - section`
  line `( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( p ) various processes relating to data management, security protocol and other technology`
  line `safeguards under clause ( m ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( q ) the procedure for issuance of new Aadhaar number to existing Aadhaar number holder under`
  line `clause ( n ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( r ) manner of authorising Registrars, enrolling agencies or other service providers to collect such`
  line `fees for services provided by them under clause ( o ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( s ) policies and practices to be followed by the Registrar, enrolling agencies and other service`
  line `providers under clause ( r ) of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23;`
  line `( t ) the manner of accessing the identity information by the Aadhaar number holder under the`
  line `proviso to sub - section ( 5 ) of section 28;`
  line `( u ) the manner of sharing the identity information, other than core biometric information, collected`
  line `or created under this Act under sub - section ( 2 ) of section 29;`
  line `( v ) the manner of alterat ion of demographic information under sub - section ( 1 ) and biometric`
  line `information under sub - section ( 2 ) of section 31;`
  line `( w ) the manner of and the time for maintaining the request for authentication and the response`
  line `thereon under sub - section ( 1 ), and the manner of obtaining, by the Aadhaar number holder, the`
  line `authentication records under sub - section ( 2 ) of section 32;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 14 of 2019 (w.e.f. 25 - 7 - 2019).`
